description: "We will leverage the Public Health Exposome (PHE) dataset, a comprehensive spatiotemporally aligned heterogenous area-level data source, to discover contextual SDoH through the application of our combinatorial approach. These contextual SDoH will be integrated into the OCHIN EHR data. A ML approach will be applied to create models for predicting HRSNs among a subset of the OCHIN population who had been screened for these factors. These ML predictive models will then be applied to identify patients with HRSNs among the other subset of the OCHIN EHR population who have never been screened. The result of this would be an OCHIN EHR dataset with complete HRSNs and comprehensive data on contextual SDoH."
